<%# Intent for this file:

Similar to how we did top 10 items in media categories with Mediaranker, 
we plan to provide 5 products under highlighted categories.

This is the code I used in Media Ranker. Will adjust for this purpose. %>

<ul>

Product.find_by category: 'Food'
Product.find_by category: 'Nature'
Product.find_by category: 'Art'


  <% 5.times do |product| %>
 
    <li>
      <h4><%= link_to product.sample.name, product_path(product) %> <small> sold by <%= product.merchant %></small></h4>
    </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>